of my assignment.

121
00:08:00,947 --> 00:08:02,608
But you're right.

122
00:08:02,815 --> 00:08:05,306
He did make a fool of himself
professionally.

123
00:08:05,518 --> 00:08:08,817
How much of a fool did he make
of himself financially?

124
00:08:09,021 --> 00:08:11,717
The judgment will just about
empty his savings.

125
00:08:11,958 --> 00:08:13,016
May I go?
FRODE: Moment.

126
00:08:13,893 --> 00:08:16,361
Your report is light in another area.

127
00:08:16,562 --> 00:08:18,257
His personal life.

128
00:08:18,464 --> 00:08:20,261
Anything you chose
not to disclose?

129
00:08:21,534 --> 00:08:23,024
Nothing that
warranted inclusion.

130
00:08:23,269 --> 00:08:24,930
Does that mean yes or no?

131
00:08:25,137 --> 00:08:29,198
I think what Miss Salander
means, and I agree,
is that everyone has a right

132
