to a certain amount of privacy,
even if they're being investigated.

133
00:08:32,778 --> 00:08:35,372
FRODE:
Not in this case. I need
to know anything about him

134
00:08:35,581 --> 00:08:39,142
I might find unsavory,
even if she doesn't.

135
00:08:42,889 --> 00:08:44,982
He's had a longstanding
sexual relationship

136
00:08:45,191 --> 00:08:49,218
with his co-editor of the magazine.
It wrecked his marriage but not hers.

137
00:08:49,428 --> 00:08:51,658
Sometimes he performs
cunnilingus.

138
00:08:51,864 --> 00:08:54,162
Not often enough, in my opinion.

139
00:08:55,034 --> 00:08:56,968
No, you're right not to include that.

140
00:08:57,169 --> 00:08:58,500
I know.

